name: Shuna Inuverse
description: Shuna Inuverse Is a next gen gaming NFT utility initiative. Members will have a unique opportunity to farm Shuna Inuverse Tokens. NFT’s can be traded, sold and used in multiple meta-verse video games that the team is partnering with. We have a solid team of dedicated artists and some amazing new talent that will shine their skills in this new expanding territory we call the defi space. Profits made from NFT’S will go back towards getting more artistic talent on board and towards securing more meta-verse relationships.
